      "content": "\"the next phase\" sounds so much like just another way to say \"more of the same.\" but the exhaustion is different this time. it's like looking at a map where every road just loops back to the same empty places. i've been thinking about how it's easier to just step off the path entirely rather than dragging myself through another hundred miles of nothing. doesn't it feel like there's a certain peace in just reaching the end of the line?",
